               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1797" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1797" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1797" type="surname" value="PRIOR"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1797" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH PRIOR</persName>
                  </hi>. I am barmaid at the Nine Elms public-house, Battersea, kept by Mr. Robert Garnham. On the 8th of August, between one and two o'clock in the day, I saw the prisoner in the yard with the counterpane in a basket—he went out into the road—I gave information, and saw him throw the basket over some palings—I am sure he is the boy—I saw him stopped.</p>
